item.title: Compiler error
item.dc:creator: @Cuber317 Cuber317
item.description:
@Cuber317 wrote:

[quote=“sk8rdude461, post:3, topic:546351”][quote author=Bl3nd link=topic=665249.msg4447208#msg4447208 date=1409443871]
Is there a class named ‘Colosseum’ in package server.game.minigames?
[/quote]
He might just have to add it into the compiler…

add “src\server\game\minigames\colosseum*.java” to your compiler, where the rest of it is.[/quote]

Thank you, That worked.

Bl3nd:

Is there a class named ‘Colosseum’ in package server.game.minigames?

Yes i do, Colosseum is minigame on this server i’m working on…
